INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (6,1,'2012-12-14 00:22:35','2012-12-14 00:22:35','','GAELIC4','','inherit','open','open','','gaelic4','','','2012-12-14 00:22:35','2012-12-14 00:22:35','',0,'http://gaelicmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/GAELIC4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2,1,'2012-12-13 23:44:21','2012-12-13 23:44:21','Gaelic Moving is an Irish owner-operated <a title=\"San Francisco Moving Company\" href=\"http://www.gaelicmoving.com/\" target=\"_blank\">San Francisco moving company</a> offering the highest quality service at competitive pricing. We are well established in the Bay Area and have a reputation for being a quick yet careful and considerate moving <a href=\"http://gaelicmoving.com/about-us/gaelic_moving_about/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-152\"><img class=\" wp-image-152 alignleft\" alt=\"gaelic_moving_about\" src=\"http://gaelicmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/gaelic_moving_about.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"430\" /></a>company. Our trained and experienced workers--mainly Irish men—are seasoned pros. We bring years of high-level experience to every job. We also bring a keen eye for furniture placement as exemplified by our continuing work with one of the top home stagers in the East Bay. From large commercial relocations to small residential moves, our excellence in the care of our work and attitude is important to us and is the driving force behind guaranteeing our clientele the excellence they deserve.\r\n\r\nNot only does being an owner operated company allow us to keep our reasonable rates in place, but it also means the level of care in our work is second to none. We are proud of our reputation and it is important to us. Repeat and referred customers comprise up most of our business. Make a wise move and call us today or email us at <a href=\"mailto:gaelicmoving@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">gaelicmoving@gmail.com</a>. We provide free online or in house estimates.\r\n\r\nThanks, Darragh and team','About Us','','publish','open','open'