rong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\nAll rates are based on a two hour minimum commitment and include one large, <a href=\"http://gaelicmoving.com/licensed-insured/\">fully insured truck and men and Cargo</a>. We include in our rate, shrinkwrap, tools to assemble/disassemble furniture, along with all pads and straps necessary for a successful move!\r\n\r\nWe also offer labour-only services. $40 per hour per man with a two hour minimum. If you are in need of a pod/truck to be packed or unloaded. Our expert knowledge will ensure that everything arrives safe and sound.','Moving Services','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-23','','','2013-01-15 22:42:01','2013-01-15 22:42:01','',17,'http://gaelicmoving.com/17-revision-23/',0,'revision','',0),(145,1,'2013-01-15 22:40:04','2013-01-15 22:40:04','We are a full service moving company. We offer straightforward moving if you pack yourself, or a full pack and move if needed. We offer moving services throughout the Bay Area including San Francisco, Oakland, Berkeley, Marin County, San Jose, Palo Alto, Redwood City, Menlo Park, Mountain View, Fremont, Pleasanton, Livermore, Walnut Creek, and most other cities.  We recommend <a title=\"san francisco moving boxes\" href=\"http://www.zippgo.com\" target=\"_blank\">ZippGo moving boxes</a> for most of your packing needs. We supply wardrobe boxes for free on the day for clothes and pillows etc. <a href=\"http://gaelicmoving.com/moving-services/gaelic_truck/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-139\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-139\" alt=\"Gaelic Moving Truck Image\" src=\"http://gaelicmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/gaelic_truck.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>We also will supply cardboard protection for Art and mirrors if we are packing your goods. Dish-packs for the fragile items too. Call <a href=\"tel:415-410-5959\" target=\"_blank\">415-410-5959</a> for more details. If using ZippGo boxes and you\'re self packing, please insure books/heavy small items 